name: Dan Kobs
text: Ordered online with two hours notice, they were a bit late. Called to follow up, they were amazingly apologetic, fixed the issue before I even had a chance to complain. Quality was excellent as usual. Only good things to say about Thier customer service. Could have been terrible, instead I'm going out of my way to compliment them.

name: James Gault
text: This is a lackluster Pizza Hut location. Food and service were merely adequate. Nothing exceptional. It is a dying business. (Long John Silvers located behind it closed permanently.)

name: Kevin Goodman
text: So unimpressed with the food. pizza was doughy, ordered garlic cheese bread, I could not believe it was a loaf of garlic bread from a grocery store with cheese melted on it. Won't make this mistake. twice

name: Valerie Bell
text: Its pizza hut.. of course its great pizza :)

text: Sad to see this place has closed
